{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fba5a2477e","title":"对中共中央答谢古巴人民社会党的电报稿的修改","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"67b9089f06","index":0,"year":1960,"month":10,"day":22,"articleId":"fba5a2477e"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"91e39a1756","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"fba5a2477e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"菲德尔·卡斯特罗，当时任古巴政府总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"81e30d7000","type":"title","text":"对中共中央容谢古巴人民社会党的电报稿的修改”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"fba5a2477e"},{"id":"91e39a1756","type":"paragraph","text":"祝您们在进一步加强革命力量的团结，保卫与推进革命的斗争中，在菲德尔·卡斯特罗英雄领袖的领导下，在反对以美帝国主义为首的侵略和战争势力、维护世界和平的斗争中获得新的胜利。要古巴，不要美国佬！打倒美国帝国主义！古巴方岁！二十个拉丁美洲国家人民方罗！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"fba5a2477e"},{"id":"216d03475d","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东对中共中央1960年10月22日答谢古巴人民社会党全国委员会祝贺中华人民共和国国庆的电报稿的修改。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"fba5a2477e"}],"page":{"id":"17cc7226e9","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"fba5a2477e","start":44,"end":44}}}},"__N_SSG":true}